[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1500","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0953","title":"WWWBoard 2.0 远程密码泄露漏洞","description":"WWWBoard 2.0 存在敏感信息泄露漏洞，其将加密后的用户密码存储在 `passwd.txt` 文件中，且该文件位于 Web 根目录下。远程攻击者无需身份认证，直接通过浏览器访问该文件路径即可获取所有用户的加密密码，进而可尝试离线破解获取明文密码，严重威胁系统安全。该漏洞影响 WWWBoard 2.0 版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0953"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:23.863","remediation":"将 passwd.txt 移至 Web 根目录之外（如 /etc/wwboard/），或通过 .htaccess 添加 `<Files passwd.txt> Deny from all</Files>` 限制访问。由于 WWWBoard 已停止维护，建议迁移至现代论坛系统（如 phpBB 或 Discourse）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0953","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/3065","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0953.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0953","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/1999/CVE-1999-0953/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-0953.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0953.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/807.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7x89-22x4-gr9x/GHSA-7x89-22x4-gr9x.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/554ca72965233bd9402be197b5470aad836fe056/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-09xx/CVE-1999-0953.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/wwwboardpwd.nasl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1500.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1500.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0707","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0707.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0907","title":"soundcard_cw 本地任意文件读取漏洞","description":"sccw（soundcard_cw）工具存在任意文件读取漏洞，本地攻击者可利用该工具读取系统上任意文件内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞源于 sccw 在文件读取操作中未对文件路径进行充分的权限校验，攻击者只需拥有本地系统访问权限即可利用，无需额外认证。CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，仅影响机密性，不影响完整性和可用性。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0907"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.287","remediation":"移除 sccw 程序的 setuid 权限位：`chmod u-s /usr/bin/sccw`。如无需使用声卡控制功能，建议直接卸载相关软件包：`apt-get remove sccw` 或 `yum remove sccw`。作为临时缓解措施，可通过 `chmod 000 /usr/bin/sccw` 禁止所有用户执行该程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0907","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b620a68f213580a6ffea66162a8ff5e007fc8af7/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0907.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0907","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0907.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6cc69bd737a75cf8d608267baabc212a8abe28cf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0907.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ebc4e3f46b7b9c5edb49036dec833178204180ea/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-79vr-x4wq-mxhp/GHSA-79vr-x4wq-mxhp.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0907.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/s