b/32372dcb4b973a68d35643516e5e8206f397c85b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0704.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0704","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0704.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/30f77465b94d71209b45a239e791a1fe062c9e8b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0704.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/1906.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/rpc.rules","https://github.com/bailehang/snort_2.2.0/blob/34f8a3a85f15645aea53d6e0d46863c7c57e43ef/doc/signatures/1905.txt","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/R/rpc_amd.nasl","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a1a39f51-3877-479a-ad5b-fc201e242044.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0333.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0888","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0888.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0817","title":"Lynx WWW 客户端 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Lynx 文本模式网页浏览器在调用外部程序处理特定协议（如 telnet）时，未对用户可控的命令行参数进行有效过滤，导致远程攻击者可构造包含恶意命令行参数的特制 URL（如 telnet:// 协议链接），诱导受害者在 Lynx 中打开，从而在受害者系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 Lynx 多个版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，属严重级别远程命令执行漏洞，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，仅需诱导用户点击恶意链接即可触发命令注入，导致任意代码执行。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0817"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:07.183","remediation":"升级 Lynx 至 2.8.1rel.2 或 2.8.2 及以上修复版本（如从源码编译请打上官方安全补丁）。临时缓解措施：在 lynx.cfg 中注释或移除 TELNET、TN3270 等外部程序调用配置（如 `TELNET_PROGRAM`），并禁止 Lynx 通过 telnet:// 等协议拉起外部程序；同时以低权限用户运行 Lynx，限制其对系统命令的调用能力。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0817","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/df06113bb625f86b49f1950d55874a29f8e76a55/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0817.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0817","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/1999/CVE-1999-0817/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0817.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0817.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-354v-9299-wg75/GHSA-354v-9299-wg75.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0817.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88360/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0888.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1686","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1686.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1053","title":"Matt Wright Guestbook.pl 服务端包含（SSI）远程命令执行漏洞","description":"guestbook.pl 是 Matt Wright 开发的 Perl CGI 留言板程序。该程序在过滤用户提交的服务器端包含（SSI）指令时，仅通过移除 \"<!--\" 与 \"-->\" 分隔符之间的内容来净化输入，过滤逻辑存在缺陷。当 guestbook.pl 运行于 Apache 1.3.9 及可能其他版本时，由于 Apache 允许使用除 \"-->\" 之外的其他闭合序列，远程攻击者可在留言中插入特制的 SSI 指令绕过过滤，从而在目标服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响使用受影响版本 guestbook.pl 并部署于存在缺陷 Apache 版本的 Web 站点，攻击条件为攻击者无需认证即可向留言板提交内容，利用方式是通过构造绕过注释闭合规则的恶意 SSI 语句实现服务端命令执行。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1053"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:36.507","remediation":"立即将 guestbook.pl 升级至 Matt Wright 官方发布的修复版本（建议 2.3.2 或更高版本），该版本已修复 SSI 过滤逻辑，可正确识别并移除所有 SSI 命令（包括非标准闭合序列）。如无法立即升级，应在 Apache 配置中对 guestbook.pl 所在目录禁用服务器端包含功能，添加 `Options -Includes` 指令阻止 SSI 解析。作为临时缓解措施，可在 guestbook.pl 脚本入口处增加输入过滤，正则匹配并删除所有包含 `#exec`、`#include`、`#config` 等 SSI 指令的内容，防止用户输入被注入执行。长期建议替换为其他维护状态活跃的留言板程序。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/33674","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/82/27296","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/82/27560","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/776","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/9907","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/1999/CVE-1999-1053.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/c2672e36893bd220d6f65c955e260796d11ed64b/1999/CVE-1999-1053.json","https://github.com/rix4uni/cvemapping/blob/ebd0bd601a59b74d0f92e5baa446be886d6ae85a/1999/CVE-1999-1053/CVE-1999-1053-PoC.py","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1053","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/5afdd8595bdd7f42c7b239ab44a422e2dd6b9f2e/1999/README.md","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/1999/CVE-1999-1053.rules","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/dde4d96d7c1eff197b9a15817af615500736afa7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1053.json","https://github.com/e-m-b-a/emba/blob/ffab8835dab57629dd708bbd389c0fd0b4f23ace/config/msf_cve-db.txt","https://github.com/diannaofengzi/POC/blob/14d504f7488db9229f6f02be54aab53e3cfee0dc/databases/1999/database/CVE-1999-1053/CVE-1999-1053-PoC-siunam321.md","https://github.com/gottburgm/Exploits/blob/fd340a05cbec416e89bfae898e27bf5fcb429101/MSFExploits/GUESTBOOK/MSF/SsiExec_infos.txt","https://github.com/siunam321/CVE-1999-1053-PoC"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1686.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1686.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1686.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0609","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0609.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0759","title":"FuseWare FuseMail 2.7 POP 邮件服务缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"此漏洞影响FuseMail 2.7版本，存在POP服务处理机制缺陷，当攻击者向目标系统发送超长USER或PASS命令时，服务器端的缓冲区缓冲区溢出，导致远程代码执行。根据CVSS评分10.0，该漏洞危害等级极高，影响范围广泛。攻击者无需任何身份验证即可远程触发此漏洞，对系统安全造成严重威胁。该漏洞由攻击者构造恶意网络请求实现，其影响可能导致完全控制目标主机。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0759"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:59.867","remediation":"立即升级到 FuseMail 2.7.1 或更高版本，该版本修复了 POP 服务中 USER/PASS 命令长度验证漏洞；并在 /etc/fusemail/fusemail.conf 中添加 \"pop_max_line_length=1024\" 配置以限制命令长度输入；如无法立即升级，可通过防火墙禁用默认 POP 端口110/995，避免外部网络访问，以及限制源IP地址范围至内部网络。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.crosswinds.net/~fuseware/faq.html#8","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/634","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19496","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e268305fd8644994d337819e469d1f89bafde833/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0759.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0759","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/1999/CVE-1999-0759/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f65723