E-1999-0255.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0249","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0689","title":"Sun Common Desktop Environment dtspcd 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"CDE（Common Desktop Environment）的 dtspcd 守护进程存在符号链接攻击漏洞，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意符号链接诱导 dtspcd 以高权限写入文件，从而覆盖系统关键文件或执行任意命令，实现本地权限提升。该漏洞影响 CDE 2.1 及 Solaris 7.0 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议升级至不受影响的版本或禁用 dtspcd 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0689"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:51.173","remediation":"建议立即安装 Sun 官方补丁 106577-01 (Solaris 7) 或 106578-01 (Solaris 7 x86)，升级 CDE 至修复版本。如无法打补丁，可在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释 dtspcd 行并重启 inetd 以禁用该服务，或限制 dtspcd 仅允许受信用户访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/636","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A1880","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19498","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/a3f034241443c2295538d03be5945be20fc1cca3/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0689","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0689.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6294b4e43a4333eb79c2542461b42377b040bdc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ec5a87b3406c3c1656cd4a2173d6654664bbeddf/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv/GHSA-wp6j-p4jf-4rwv.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--c3dc2ea0-0265-4c0c-ae08-6be3c238c97a.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0689.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0249.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0249.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0246","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0246.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0687","title":"CDE ToolTalk ttsession 守护进程远程代码执行漏洞","description":"ToolTalk ttsession 守护进程存在 RPC 认证缺陷，由于使用了弱 RPC 认证机制，远程攻击者无需有效认证即可向该服务发送恶意请求，利用该漏洞可在目标系统上以 ttsession 进程权限执行任意命令。该漏洞影响多个 Unix 操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。建议升级到包含修复的版本或禁用 ToolTalk 服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0687"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.907","remediation":"立即停止并禁用 ttsession 守护进程（ToolTalk 服务），该服务默认监听 RPC 端口。如业务不需要 ToolTalk 功能，执行 `/etc/init.d/dtlogin stop` 并移除相关启动项。在防火墙上限制对 RPC 端口映射服务（111/TCP,UDP）和 ToolTalk 动态端口的入站访问，仅允许可信主机通信。对于必须使用 ToolTalk 的环境，升级到 Sun 安全公告 192 对应的补丁版本（Solaris 2.5.1/2.6/7），或迁移至已修复此漏洞的 Solaris 8 及以上版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/192","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/k-001.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/637","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9909-103","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/985d46f062894917f05cdf3d64399a32839d12b7/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0687.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0687","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0687.md","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/588.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a6294b4e43a4333eb79c2542461b42377b040bdc/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0687.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/619496beb1911717821b542248e7d44ebd98cfb6/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-r6jq-jwxp-368g/GHSA-r6jq-jwxp-368g.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/rpc.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/chamara84/snort-2.9_RTDS/blob/893942516b660280cc187ddf79d13fca72df6a20/snort-2.9.14.1/doc/signatures/1299.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88351/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0246.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1194","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1194.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1575","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":10368,\"inputTokens\":584,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10973}}","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.01/5.0 中多个 ActiveX 控件（Kodak/Wang Image Edit、Image Annotation、Image Scan、Thumbnail Image、Image Admin、HHOpen、Registration Wizard、IE Active Setup）被错误标记为\"安全可脚本\"，且存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可构造恶意网页诱导用户访问，触发 setupctl.dll 等控件的缓冲区溢出，在用户当前权限下创建/修改文件并执行任意命令。影响 Windows 95/NT 4.0 系统上的 IE 4.01/5.0，CVSS 5.1 中危，需用户交互才能利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1575"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:45.250","remediation":"升级到 Microsoft Internet Explorer 5.5 或更高版本（安装对应 Windows 95/NT 4.0 的最新累积安全补丁）。如无法立即升级，可在 IE 安全设置中将\"对未标记为可安全执行脚本的 ActiveX 控件初始化和脚本运行\"设为\"禁用\"，并在注册表中将 imgedit.ocx、imgscan.ocx、imgthumb.ocx、imgadmin.ocx、hhopen.ocx、regwizc.dll、setupctl.dll 对应 Kill Bit 设为 0x00000400 以禁用这些控件作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/23412","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/24839","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/26924","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/41408","http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/9162","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/28719","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-037","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/7097","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19515","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1575.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1575","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1575.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1575.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-47wv-vjpm-2h95/GHSA-47wv-vjpm-2h95.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87944/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--a79cec69-fa4e-4d67-8715-d3ad5c1620c5.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000770.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1194.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0309","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0309.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0702","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 导入导出收藏夹功能远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.0.1/5.0/5.01 的\"导入/导出收藏夹\"功能存在代码注入漏洞（CWE-94）。远程攻击者可通过诱导用户打开或导入特制收藏夹文件（.html/.url 格式），利用 ImportExportFavorites 特性向目标系统写入恶意文件或直接执行任意代码，且代码以当前用户权限运行。该漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，攻击复杂度低。受影响版本包括 IE 4.0.1、IE 5.0 和 IE 5.01，CVSS v2 评分为满分 10.0，危害等级严重。Microsoft 于 1999 年 9 月发布 MS99-037 安全公告及 KB241361 补丁修复该漏洞，建议受影响用户尽快升级 IE 至安全版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0702"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.797","remediation":"建议立即将 Internet Explorer 升级至 5.5 或以上版本（通过 Windows Update 安装 Microsoft 1999 年 11 月累积安全补丁），或安装对应安全更新。如暂无法升级，可在「Internet 选项 → 安全」中将 Internet 区域安全级别设为高，禁用「文件下载」与「运行 ActiveX 控件和插件」，并通过组策略限制 Favorites 导入导出功能，同时避免访问不可信网页作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ241361","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/627","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-037","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19490","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/32372dcb4b973a68d35643516e5e8206f397c85b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0702.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0702","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/3a4e4ec8f851966b650deff569d0a9bd2796dd18/1999/CVE-1999-0702/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0702.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/30f77465b94d71209b45a239e791a1fe062c9e8b/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0702.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/c9462134bd15c86fd0ed45fb18bd761cdf938c73/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2q7j-jrwg-8822/GHSA-2q7j-jrwg-8822.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0702.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0309.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0309.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0309.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1091","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1091.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1377","title":"Matt Wright download.cgi 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"download.cgi 1.0 存在路径遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 f 参数传入 `../` 等目录跳转序列，绕过访问限制读取服务器上的任意文件。该漏洞源于程序未对用户输入的文件路径进行充分过滤和规范化处理，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，可能导致敏感配置文件、系统文件等泄露。影响运行 Matt Wright's download.cgi 1.0 的 Web 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1377"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:18.610","remediation":"立即停止使用 Matt Wright 的 download.cgi 1.0 脚本，该脚本已停止维护且无安全更新。彻底删除服务器上所有 download.cgi 文件，或通过 Web 服务器配置（如 Apache 的 <Location> 指令）限制对该脚本的访问。如必须使用，在 CGI 脚本中对 f 参数进行路径规范化过滤，拒绝包含 ../ 或 %2e%2e/ 等目录遍历序列的输入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://pulhas.org/phrack/55/P55-07.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1091.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0273","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0273.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0697","title":"SCO Doctor 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SCO Doctor 管理工具中存在权限提升漏洞，本地用户可通过该工具的 \"Tools\" 选项以 root 权限执行任意操作。攻击者需拥有系统本地访问权限，利用该漏洞可完全控制受影响系统，包括修改系统配置、访问敏感数据及安装恶意程序。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 等版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户限制本地用户对 SCO Doctor 工具的访问权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0697"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.187","remediation":"升级 SCO OpenServer 至 5.0.5 及以上版本，或安装 SCO 官方安全补丁 erg712103。如无法升级，移除 SCO Doctor 的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /opt/K/SCO/Doctor/1.0.0/bin/doctor），并限制可登录系统的本地用户账号数量，仅保留管理员可交互登录。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/621","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0697","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0697.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-fwr5-hvj8-gff6/GHSA-fwr5-hvj8-gff6.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0697.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-datase